    {
      "id": "fff0bb8d-7a39-4693-8109-b8184805a0db",
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "Example 1: Implement a class named FUV_student can be initialized with first name, last name, and student ID has a method get_FUV_email that returns the student email.\n\nclass FUV_student:\n    def __init__(self, first_name, last_name, student_id):\n        self.first_name = first_name\n        self.last_name = last_name\n        self.student_id = student_id\n\n    def get_FUV_email(self):\n        # Example format: firstname.lastname@student.fulbright.edu.vn\n        return self.first_name + '.' + self.last_name + '@student.fulbright.edu.vn'\n\n# Example usage\ns = FUV_student(\"Khoi\", \"Bui\", \"123456\")\nprint(s.get_FUV_email())",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "markdown",
        "id": "fff0bb8d-7a39-4693-8109-b8184805a0db"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "d2e9153b-b13b-418f-85fd-810138c2c538",
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "class FUV_student{\r\n    public String first_name; //fields or attributes\r\n    public String last_name;\r\n    public String student_id;\r\n    public FUV_student(String first_name, String  last_name, String  student_id){\r\n        this.first_name = first_name;\r\n        this.last_name = last_name;\r\n        this.student_id = student_id;}\r\n\r\n    public String get_FUV_email(){\r\n        // Example format: firstname.lastname@student.fulbright.edu.vn\r\n        return this.first_name + \".\" \r\n            + this.last_name +\".\"+ this.student_id  \r\n            + \"@student.fulbright.edu.vn\";}\r\n    }\r\nFUV_student s = new FUV_student(\"Khoi\", \"Bui\", \"123456\");\r\nIO.print(s.get_FUV_email());\r\n",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "java",
        "id": "d2e9153b-b13b-418f-85fd-810138c2c538",
        "executionSummary": {
          "executionOrder": 26,
          "success": true
        }
      },
      "execution_count": 26,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "execute_result",
          "data": {
            "text/plain": "Khoi.Bui.123456@student.fulbright.edu.vn"
          },
          "metadata": {},
          "execution_count": 26
        }
      ]
    },
